 7 | f4808080 f4808080 f4808080 f4808080 f4808080 f4808080 f4808080 |􀀀􀀀􀀀􀀀􀀀􀀀􀀀
14 | ...
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.sp
