.B pytermor.parser.ESCAPE_SEQ_REGEX
Regular expression that matches all classes of escape sequences.
.sp
More specifically, it recognizes \fBnF\fP, \fBFp\fP, \fBFe\fP and \fBFs\fP [1] 
